Thanks to the creators and maintainers of the packages, we are using:

- libcurl (Daniel Stenberg) for 
the HTTP 1.1, FTP, telnet, ldap, etc client stacks;

- openssl for the TLS/SSL stack;

- dialog package for the console dialog menu;

- libevent (Niels Provos) for the 
I/O event demultiplexing framework;

- iprouted2, 
netlink and the whole 
linux netdev for 
linux TCP/IP stack (Alexey Kuznetsov, David Miller and many others).
